<body>

    <h1 style="font-size:400%;text-align:center;color:crimson"> Ultimate Date Night Planner</h1>
    <br />
    <p style="font-size:150%">
        Have you ever had a first date and you don't know where to start planning it?  You will be happy to know that
        you have come to the right place.  This website will take the stress out of planning a first date.
    </p>
    <br />
    <div>
        <h3 style="font-size:400%"> First Date Quizzes <img src="~/Images/quiz.png" style="height:150px;width:250px;vertical-align:bottom;margin-left:80px" /> </h3>
        Before going on a first date, it is always good to know your love personality and get help with what to wear.
        The following two quizzes will help you to prepare for a first date in order to ensure a second date! <br />
        <div class="row">
            <div class="column">
                Love Personality Quiz: <button onclick="location.href='/Date/Quiz'" style="background-color:lightblue">Take Quiz</button><br />
            </div>
            <div class="column">
                Style Quiz: <button onclick="location.href='/Date/StyleQuiz'" style="background-color:lightblue">Take Quiz</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr style="height:2px;border-width:0;color:crimson;background-color:crimson">
    </div>
    <br />
    <div>
        <h3 style="font-size:400%">
            Need an Icebreaker?<img src="~/Images/icebreaker.png" style="height:150px;width:300px;vertical-align:bottom;margin-left:200px" />
        </h3>
        First dates are always difficult. You never know what to say or what to talk about.  We are here to help.  You can
        find a funny joke to break the ice or some trivia based on your favorite category. <br />
        <button onclick="location.href='/Date/IceBreakers'" style="background-color:lightblue">Get Icebreakers</button>
        <hr style="height:2px;border-width:0;color:crimson;background-color:crimson">
    </div>
    <br />
    <br />
    <div>
        <h3 style="font-size:400%">Weather  <img src="~/Images/sun.jpg" style="height:150px;width:300px;vertical-align:bottom;margin-left:200px" /></h3>
        Knowing what the weather is going to be like is critical! Make sure your date doesn't end up rained out and you
        are attired appropriately. Get a three day weather forecast. <br />
        <button onclick="location.href='/Date/WeatherIndex'" style="background-color:lightblue">Weather</button>
        <hr style="height:2px;border-width:0;color:crimson;background-color:crimson">
    </div>
    <br />
    <br />

    <h3 style="font-size:400%"> Unsure what to do?<img src="~/Images/sailing.jpg" style="height:150px;width:300px;vertical-align:bottom;margin-left:100px"/></h3>
    <p>
        Planning the perfect date is always difficult, especially if you don't really know the other person.  How about
        looking for an event, movie, activity or restaurant.
    </p>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="column">
            <h5>Events</h5>

            Going to an event is always a fun idea.  From a music concert to a sports game, there is always something to do! <br />
            <button onclick="location.href='/Date/EventIndex'" style="background-color:lightblue">Events</button>
            <br />
            <br />

            <h5>Movies</h5>

            Movies are always a safe bet.  Many first dates start with a movie and seeing a movie is perfect if you are shy
            or really don't know your date's interests.<br />
            <button onclick="location.href='/Date/MovieIndex'" style="background-color:lightblue">Movies</button>
        </div>
        <div class="column">
            <h5>Activities</h5>

            If you prefer something a little more active and know some of your date's interests, an activity is the perfect
            date for you. You can go compete in a game of bowling or golf, go to a museum, go to the beach, or whatever other
            activity you can think of.<br />
            <button onclick="location.href='/Date/ActivityIndex'" style="background-color:lightblue">Activities</button>
            <br />
            <br />
            <h5>Restaurants</h5>

            No date is complete without something to eat. Either before you go see that movie or after a game of bowling,
            going to a restaurant is a must.  Find your favorite cuisine here.<br />
            <button onclick="location.href='/Date/RestaurantIndex'" style="background-color:lightblue">Restaurants</button>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>   